This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with modelling human free-hand sketches and their relationship with photo edge-maps. Additionally, the paper proposes a deep FG-SBIR model which is a common task in computer vision. 

The paper also involves unsupervised image style transfer, which falls under the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. 

The use of deep learning models in the paper suggests that it could also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category. 

The paper involves geometric projections and matching of sketches to photos, which could fall under the Graphics (cs.GR) sub-category. 

Finally, the paper involves image processing and manipulation, which could fall under the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
